1.Environment and tools:

	springboot
	postgreSQL

2.Database:
	roleName=jervis
	databaseName=jervis
	password=jervis

3.Host Port:
	port=9393
	host=http://localhost:9393/...
	The port can be changed on (src/main/webapp/static/js/app.js) the 3rd line.

4.All settings in application.properties

5.Basic API
	main page: GET-> host/index 
	get all beers: GET-> host/all
	get random beer: GET-> host/random
	add new beer: POST-> host/beer
	remove beers: POST-> host/remove